# 二、增加一个读取 JdbcTemplate 参数的方法

这个方法只支持你截图中的场景：

```java
jdbcTemplate.query(
        sql,
        new Object[]{systemName},
        rowMapper
);
```

代码：

```java
private List<PositionalSourceParameter> resolveJdbcTemplateParameters(
        final Path javaSourceFile,
        final String methodName) {

    try {
        final CompilationUnit compilationUnit =
                StaticJavaParser.parse(javaSourceFile);

        return compilationUnit.findAll(MethodDeclaration.class).stream()
                .filter(method -> method.getNameAsString().equals(methodName))
                .findFirst()
                .map(this::extractJdbcTemplateParameters)
                .orElseGet(Collections::emptyList);

    } catch (final Exception exception) {
        LOGGER.warn(
                "Failed to resolve JdbcTemplate positional parameters. file={}, method={}, reason={}",
                javaSourceFile,
                methodName,
                exception.getMessage());

        return Collections.emptyList();
    }
}
```

再增加：

```java
private List<PositionalSourceParameter> extractJdbcTemplateParameters(
        final MethodDeclaration method) {

    final Map<String, String> methodParameterTypes =
            method.getParameters().stream()
                    .collect(Collectors.toMap(
                            Parameter::getNameAsString,
                            parameter -> parameter.getType().asString(),
                            (first, second) -> first,
                            LinkedHashMap::new));

    return method.findAll(MethodCallExpr.class).stream()
            .filter(call -> call.getNameAsString().equals("query"))
            .flatMap(call -> call.getArguments().stream())
            .filter(Expression::isArrayCreationExpr)
            .map(Expression::asArrayCreationExpr)
            .filter(array -> array.getInitializer().isPresent())
            .findFirst()
            .map(array -> array.getInitializer()
                    .orElseThrow()
                    .getValues()
                    .stream()
                    .map(Expression::toString)
                    .map(parameterName -> new PositionalSourceParameter(
                            parameterName,
                            methodParameterTypes.getOrDefault(
                                    parameterName,
                                    "Object")))
                    .toList())
            .orElseGet(Collections::emptyList);
}
```

需要 imports：

```java
import com.github.javaparser.ast.body.Parameter;
import com.github.javaparser.ast.expr.Expression;
import com.github.javaparser.ast.expr.MethodCallExpr;
```

`CompilationUnit`、`MethodDeclaration`、`Collectors` 你大概率已经有。

