# 三、只修改现有 `resolvePositionalParameters()`

你当前方法大概是：

```java
private Map<Integer, ResolvedParameter> resolvePositionalParameters(
        final NativeSqlRecord record) {

    if (record == null || record.getParameterCount() <= 0) {
        return Collections.emptyMap();
    }

    final Map<Integer, ResolvedParameter> resolvedParameters =
            new LinkedHashMap<>();

    final List<String> parameterNames = record.getParameterNames();

    for (int index = 1;
         index <= record.getParameterCount();
         index++) {

        final String parameterName =
                index <= parameterNames.size()
                        ? parameterNames.get(index - 1)
                        : "arg" + index;

        final boolean collection =
                looksLikeCollectionParameter(parameterName);

        resolvedParameters.put(
                index,
                createResolvedParameter(parameterName, collection));
    }

    return resolvedParameters;
}
```

改成下面这个 MVP 版本：

```java
private Map<Integer, ResolvedParameter> resolvePositionalParameters(
        final NativeSqlRecord record) {

    if (record == null || record.getParameterCount() <= 0) {
        return Collections.emptyMap();
    }

    final Optional<Path> javaSourceFile =
            projectPathResolver.resolveJavaSourceFile(record);

    final List<PositionalSourceParameter> sourceParameters =
            javaSourceFile
                    .map(path -> resolveJdbcTemplateParameters(
                            path,
                            record.getMethodName()))
                    .orElseGet(Collections::emptyList);

    final Map<Integer, ResolvedParameter> resolvedParameters =
            new LinkedHashMap<>();

    final List<String> inventoryParameterNames =
            record.getParameterNames() == null
                    ? Collections.emptyList()
                    : record.getParameterNames();

    for (int index = 1;
         index <= record.getParameterCount();
         index++) {

        if (index <= sourceParameters.size()) {
            final PositionalSourceParameter sourceParameter =
                    sourceParameters.get(index - 1);

            resolvedParameters.put(
                    index,
                    createResolvedParameterFromJavaType(
                            sourceParameter.parameterName(),
                            sourceParameter.javaType()));

            continue;
        }

        final String fallbackParameterName =
                index <= inventoryParameterNames.size()
                        ? inventoryParameterNames.get(index - 1)
                        : "arg" + index;

        final boolean collection =
                looksLikeCollectionParameter(fallbackParameterName);

        resolvedParameters.put(
                index,
                createResolvedParameter(
                        fallbackParameterName,
                        collection));
    }

    return resolvedParameters;
}
```

逻辑非常清楚：

```text
能从 new Object[]{...} 解析
    → 使用真实方法参数名和类型
    → HIGH confidence

解析不到
    → 保留现有旧逻辑
    → LOW confidence
```

